to address climate change.

00:15:49.320 --> 00:15:54.520
CURBELO: And what I would tell
my friends in public office
is we need your leadership,

00:15:54.560 --> 00:15:56.189
both sides of the aisle.

00:15:56.189 --> 00:15:58.424
Doesn't matter
if you're Republican,
Democrat, Independent,

00:15:58.424 --> 00:16:02.094
you have a role to play
here and those of us who
are from Florida should

00:16:02.094 --> 00:16:08.167
be even more active and
aggressive in pursuing these
policies because you know

00:16:08.167 --> 00:16:10.269
what's bad for jobs
and the economy?

00:16:10.269 --> 00:16:16.120
Sea level rise and coastal
flooding and saltwater
intrusion into the Everglades

00:16:16.280 --> 00:16:19.560
where our drinking supply
rests in South Florida.

00:16:20.046 --> 00:16:22.281
That will really
devastate our region.

00:16:22.281 --> 00:16:26.219
It actually won't allow
