 absorb rainwater,

00:55:52.983 --> 00:55:55.819
creating an elevated risk
 of floods and mudslides.

00:55:56.653 --> 00:55:58.422
MAN: Oh my God!

00:55:59.823 --> 00:56:02.059
NARRATOR: The mudslides,
 combined with almost 9,000
 wildfires that burned through

00:56:02.060 --> 00:56:10.040
